    <item>
      <title>墨西哥央行行长罗德里格斯暗示仍有进一步降息的“空间”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/banxico-governor-rodriguez-signals-openness-to-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥央行行长维多利亚·罗德里格斯表示，比索本月的波动影响了央行周四维持利率不变的决定。鉴于其可能对通胀产生的影响，它也可能影响央行如何权衡未来的降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/banxico-governor-rodriguez-signals-openness-to-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度开始纳入债券市场，将受到更多全球关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/india-set-for-greater-global-attention-as-bond-inclusion-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司将于周五将印度政府债券纳入其新兴市场指数，从而向更广泛的投资者开放 1.3 万亿美元的市场，印度将吸引数十亿美元的资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/india-set-for-greater-global-attention-as-bond-inclusion-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市上涨，收益率下跌，因个人消费支出推动美联储降息押注：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储青睐的通胀指标降温，增强了人们对政策制定者今年将有降息空间的预期，股票期货上涨，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 22:31:19 GMT</pubDate>
